{"id":"clm_622bd94ec569f00e","text":"These are the same standardisation levers, not yet pulled, that the animal field has debated for decades, and they depend on automation and biobanking to make organoid generation reproducible at scale.","section":"sec-nams-data","anchor":"content/06_nams_data.md#clm_622bd94ec569f00e","claimType":"methodological","qualification":"Source claim type: methodological; modality: likely; scope status: minor_difference_qualified.","scope":{"population":"organoid generation","model":"organoid generation","outcome":"reproducibility-at-scale parallels with the animal field","method":"standardisation, automation, biobanking"}}
